\nIf a patient declines to respond, do not code based on proxy response or medical record documentation. \n\nIf the patient can provide a response: \n\nOASIS-E1 \nEffective 01/01/2025 \nCenters for Medicare & Medicaid Services \n\n20", "type": "Document"}}